<div class="your-rights">
    <div class="chevron-div"><img class="chevron" src="chevron-double-right.png"></div>
    <div class="question-div"><b><p class="title">If officers enter your home without your permission<br> Remembr the following:</p></b></div>

      <div class="rights-container">
        <ul>
            <li><p>Do not resist. You have the right to state that you did not consent to their entry, that you will exercise your right to remain silent, and to request a lawyer. Anyone else in your home also has the right to remain silent.</p></li>

            <li><p>Do not show any false documents (IDs, birth certificates, etc.) to the officers.</p></li>

            <li><u><p>Do not sign any papers prior to speaking with a lawyer.</p></u></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
